{"tid":1889793,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"阿Sir恨左粒花好耐，終於攞到","createTime":"2020-02-20T21:02:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T01:00:17.000Z","uid":14503,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"96299177342650414cf9c74135e2ada06473b87a","tid":1889793,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T21:02:02.000Z","msg":"仲要唔止一粒，不過係個肺度<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a657101a10cdc8db74c2c0f6494bd3b3a9529e1f","tid":1889793,"uid":6058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T00:53:19.000Z","msg":"遲下唔喺個肺到<br />\n而係墳頭頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c14fe27691a2e2fe147469906101ecf53ac22abf","tid":1889793,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T00:55:27.000Z","msg":"認真睇哂佢plz <br />\n<br />\nTerry Yeung:<br />\n新聞跑來了。「文宣平台」複製貼上，再推農場內容謀利；兩登網友群起轉發，內容被一覽無遺。<br />\n<br />\n點擊沒了，連帶的商業價值都被抹殺。有些媒體，如《蘋果》，更是走會員制。<br />\n<br />\n試問，你忽然尊重的媒體工作者，要怎樣謀生？<br />\n<br />\n半年來，愈見惡化。議題被網民壞習慣，以及網軍的無形之手操控。<br />\n<br />\n然後你說：運動靜咗好多。<br />\n<br />\n改變自己，改變習慣。<br />\n<br />\n1. 不是正統媒體的新聞，不轉發。<br />\n2. 未經Fact Check、來自內容農場的消息，不要理。<br />\n3. 很多文宣大台都是盜取內容，不轉發。<br />\n4. 只轉發原創者的內容<br />\n5. 貼報道上討論區，只取少量內容，放link鼓勵點擊（尢其文宣大台該帶頭做）。<br />\n<br />\n再重覆，目標為上，才可以拯救連登垂死的熱門。<br />\n<br />\n比方說，<br />\n1. 如果兩日後有遊行，專注推行動Post；<br />\n2. 同一議題，集中處理，不要分散；<br />\n3. 有人留言「拉」，網友不需再留言；<br />\n4. 戒除政治J女性癖，不要再討論區議員身材；<br />\n5. 未能Fact Check的事情，忍痛讓佢沉。<br />\n6. 減少用極端字眼，例如「就嚟輸」；<br />\n7. 至為重要：不 要 再 推 假 標 題<br />\n<br />\n每個手足都有責任打好呢場資訊戰，改變習慣，重奪輿論主導權，大家一定做得到。<br />\n<br />\nYoutube戰線：黃色資訊片一律Coment+Like+Share&amp;Subscribe（CLS)（share做唔到的話重要片先share)<br />\n<br />\n香港人，改變。<br />\n<br />\nP.S.如果覺得有意思，煩請分享，謝謝你。<br />\n-------------------------------------------<br />\nIG：Terry_yeung_blog<br />\nIG連結：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2IMS6HI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IMS6HI&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqF8v4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=698a9e7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2IMS6HI</a>"},{"pid":"df0af9890ebfe333924dd7f7d4e8287b4b8ba571","tid":1889793,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a657101a10cdc8db74c2c0f6494bd3b3a9529e1f","tid":1889793,"uid":6058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T00:53:19.000Z","msg":"遲下唔喺個肺到<br />\n而係墳頭頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T00:55:53.000Z","msg":"大大札<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04bb58330a08a896da7cc9250a699f8ee8531036","tid":1889793,"uid":222970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T01:00:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rDF8OnD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrDF8OnD.jpg&h=38bb4a48&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}